  "detailed_description": "The Wyverns are gone...<br><br>Now your home is plunged into chaos as monsters invade from their world as a new recruit to the mercenary guild you must tackle this threat head on. Without the protection of the wyvern only you stand between them and the destruction of Wyvia. <br><br>Find the source of the monster invasion, discover where the all wyverns have gone, and unlock the power hidden away in you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/349398b7b9f36e5ebf45e9f36b7c268f.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a3659bbd61c6be4b210b76dc974269cb.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a3659bbd61c6be4b210b76dc974269cb.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a3659bbd61c6be4b210b76dc974269cb.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wyvia features fun and simple combat that feels good to utilize! Whack Goopies with a huge axe or fire away with screen clearing abilities!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/05a8a6bcf970b568f9fe5a1842ea3684.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mix and match skills between 10 distinct classes, allocate points into stats and skills, and create a character that's really your own!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/1a1c0a14d019c458c13d731c39f5556e.avif?t=1752862811\" width=606 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a variety of locations from plains, deep caves, spooky forests, and frozen wastes as you struggle against the invasion of monsters in your world and find the source of their intrusion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/84493b8eead9e4b41f054cf014880396.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=107 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ab19ad93bebbc1a60e08332b5b93099b.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ab19ad93bebbc1a60e08332b5b93099b.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ab19ad93bebbc1a60e08332b5b93099b.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use the power of Wyverns to fly, gain new abilities, augment your combat prowess and explore the world around you.",
  "about_the_game": "The Wyverns are gone...<br><br>Now your home is plunged into chaos as monsters invade from their world as a new recruit to the mercenary guild you must tackle this threat head on. Without the protection of the wyvern only you stand between them and the destruction of Wyvia. <br><br>Find the source of the monster invasion, discover where the all wyverns have gone, and unlock the power hidden away in you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/349398b7b9f36e5ebf45e9f36b7c268f.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a3659bbd61c6be4b210b76dc974269cb.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a3659bbd61c6be4b210b76dc974269cb.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/a3659bbd61c6be4b210b76dc974269cb.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wyvia features fun and simple combat that feels good to utilize! Whack Goopies with a huge axe or fire away with screen clearing abilities!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/05a8a6bcf970b568f9fe5a1842ea3684.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=147 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/fdd2bce3963f89e24fdad7eeaf205644.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mix and match skills between 10 distinct classes, allocate points into stats and skills, and create a character that's really your own!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/1a1c0a14d019c458c13d731c39f5556e.avif?t=1752862811\" width=606 height=146 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.webm?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ce3a5639421270d41f9bc1448658d59d.mp4?t=1752862811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a variety of locations from plains, deep caves, spooky forests, and frozen wastes as you struggle against the invasion of monsters in your world and find the source of their intrusion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/84493b8eead9e4b41f054cf014880396.avif?t=1752862811\" width=608 height=107 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579660/extras/ab19ad93bebbc1a60e08332b5b93099b.poster.avif?t=1752862811\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steam